{"version": "https://jsonfeed.org/version/1", "title": "Hiraeth's Wiki", "home_page_url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/", "feed_url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/feed_json_updated.json", "description": "My personal wiki", "icon": null, "authors": [{"name": "hiraeth"}], "language": "en", "items": [{"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/About/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/About/", "title": "About", "content_html": "<h1>About This Wiki</h1>\n<p>Publish your public notes with MkDocs</p>\n<h2>Hello World!</h2>\n<p>The <code>index.md</code> in the <code>/docs</code> folder is the homepage you see here.</p>\n<p>The folders in...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/3in1wiki/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/3in1wiki/", "title": "\u7528mkdocs\u3001obsidian\u3001zotero\u642d\u5efa\u4e2a\u4ebawiki", "content_html": "<h1>\u4f7f\u7528mkdocs\u3001obsidian\u3001zotero\u642d\u5efa\u4e2a\u4eba\u5728\u7ebfwiki</h1>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/archinstall/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/archinstall/", "title": "\u53cc\u7cfb\u7edf\u5b89\u88c5archlinux", "content_html": "<h1>Basic installation of arch linux</h1>\n<p>\u53cc\u7cfb\u7edf\u5b89\u88c5archlinux\uff0c\u4f7f\u7528btrfs\u6587\u4ef6\u7cfb\u7edf\u3002\u91cd\u88c5\u7cfb\u7edf\u7684\u4e2a\u4eba\u53c2\u8003\u3002</p>\n<h2>\u542f\u52a8\u76d8</h2>\n<p>\u4e0b\u8f7darchlinux\u7684iso\u6587\u4ef6\u3002\u627e\u4e00\u4e2aU\u76d8\uff0c\u7528 <code>ventoy</code>\u5b89\u88c5\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u628aiso\u653e\u8fdb\u53bb\u3002</p>\n<p>\u53ef\u4ee5\u5148\u5728win\u4e0b\u7528  <kbd>win</kbd>+...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["arch"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/format/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/format/", "title": "Text Formatting", "content_html": "<h1>Text Formatting</h1>\n<p>You can have lists like this</p>\n<ul>\n<li>first</li>\n<li>second</li>\n<li>third</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Or checklist lists to</p>\n<ul>\n<li>[ ] ==Get==</li>\n<li>[ ] things</li>\n<li>[ ] ~~done~~</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, get highl...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/git/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/git/", "title": "git\u5907\u5fd8", "content_html": "<h2>submodule</h2>\n<p>\u5047\u5b9a\u6211\u4eec\u6709\u4e24\u4e2a\u9879\u76ee\uff1a<code>project-main</code> \u548c <code>project-sub-1</code>\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d <code>project-main</code> \u8868\u793a\u4e3b\u9879\u76ee\uff0c\u800c <code>project-sub-1</code> \u8868\u793a\u5b50\u6a21\u5757\u9879\u76ee\u3002</p>\n<p>\u5176\u4e2d <code>project-main</code> \u7684\u8fdc\u7a0b\u4ed3\u5e93\u5730\u5740\u4e3a `https://github.com/u...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["git"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/latex/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/latex/", "title": "LaTeX Math Support", "content_html": "<h1>LaTeX Math Support</h1>\n<p>LaTeX math is supported using MathJax.</p>\n<p>Inline math looks like $f(x) = x^2$. The input for this is <code>$f(x) = x^2$</code>. Use <code>$...$</code>.</p>\n<p>For a ...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/mermaid/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/mermaid/", "title": "Mermaid diagrams", "content_html": "<h1>Mermaid diagrams</h1>\n<p>Here's the example from <a href=\"https://squidfunk.github.io/mkdocs-material/reference/diagrams/#using-flowcharts\">MkDocs Material documentation</a>...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/obsidian/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/obsidian/", "title": "obsidian", "content_html": "<h1>obsidian</h1>\n<h2>Install</h2>\n<h2>plugins</h2>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["hexo", "obsidian", "wikitten", "zotero"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/wikitten/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/wikitten/", "title": "wikitten", "content_html": "<h1>Using hexo and wikitten to deploy online wiki</h1>\n<h2>hexo</h2>\n<h2>wikitten</h2>\n<h2>deploy</h2>\n<h2>obsidian</h2>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["hexo"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/zotero/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Code/zotero/", "title": "zotero", "content_html": "<h1>Zotero</h1>\n<h2>Install</h2>\n<h2>Plugins</h2>\n<p><strong>zotero 7:</strong>\n- zotmoov\n- zotero better notes</p>\n<p>Both:</p>\n<h2>Sync</h2>\n<p>zotero 7 to rename:\n```\n{{ title case=\"snake\" }}{{ authors ...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["obsidian", "wiki", "zotero"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Life/cocktail/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Life/cocktail/", "title": "cocktail", "content_html": "<h1>Cocktail</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Drink properly</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>\u5173\u4e8e\u9e21\u5c3e\u9152\u7684\u5c0f\u77e5\u8bc6</p>\n<h2>\u7406\u8bba\u90e8\u5206</h2>\n<p>\u300a\u9e21\u5c3e\u9152\u6cd5\u5178\u300b\u5c06\u6240\u6709\u8c03\u9152\u5206\u4e3a6\u4e2a\u6846\u67b6\uff0c\u5373\u6240\u6709\u65e0\u8bba\u662f\u591a\u4e48\u82b1\u91cc\u80e1\u54e8\u7684\u9152\u90fd\u662f\u5efa\u7acb\u5728\u8be5\u79cd\u57fa\u7840\u4e0a\u7684\u3002\n1. <code>old fashioned</code> \u5373\u53e4\u5178\u7c7b\u9e21\u5c3e\u9152\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u53e4\u5178\u9e21\u5c3e\u9152\u66fe\u662f\u6240\u6709\u9e21\u5c3e\u9152\u7684\u4ee3\u540d\u8bcd\uff0c\u572819\u4e16\u7eaa\u521d\u9e21\u5c3e\u9152\u521a\u51fa\u73b0\u65f6\uff0c...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["alcohol"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Life/iba/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Life/iba/", "title": "IBA\u9152\u8c31", "content_html": "<h1>IBA</h1>\n<h2>\u5199\u5728\u524d\u9762</h2>\n<h3>\u6240\u8c13\u300cIBA\u300d</h3>\n<p>\u300cIBA\u300d\u662f\u56fd\u9645\u8c03\u9152\u5e08\u534f\u4f1a\uff08International Bartenders Association\uff09\u7684\u7f29\u5199\uff0c\u622a\u6b62\u81f32022\u5e74\uff0c\u517190\u6b3e\u9e21\u5c3e\u9152\u88abIBA\u5b98\u65b9\u6536\u5f55\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d\u5206\u4e3a3\u4e2a\u7cfb\u5217\uff1a\u96be\u5fd8\u7ecf\u517833\u6b3e\uff08The Unforgettables\uff09\uff0c\u5f53\u4ee3\u7ecf\u517831\u6b3e\uff08Con...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["alcohol"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Math/Moduli/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Math/Moduli/", "title": "Topics in Moduli", "content_html": "<h1>note default page</h1>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["README"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Math/Moduli/sample-a1/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Math/Moduli/sample-a1/", "title": "Topics in Moduli, sample", "content_html": "<h1>Heading A1</h1>\n<h2>Sub-Heading A1 1</h2>\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nunc fringilla volutpat odio, nec iaculis tortor laoreet vitae. S...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["sample"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Math/PreBCHM/2/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/Math/PreBCHM/2/", "title": 2, "content_html": "", "image": null, "date_modified": "2024-10-17T11:23:13+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": []}, {"id": "ht